'''''The American Journal of Medicine''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] and the official journal of the [[Association of Professors of Medicine]]. It publishes original [[clinical research]] in [[internal medicine]]. It is published monthly by [[Elsevier]] under its [[Excerpta Medica]] imprint.

== Abstracting and indexing ==
The journal is abstracted and indexed in [[BIOSIS Previews|BIOSIS]], [[CINAHL]], [[Chemical Abstracts Service|Chemical Abstracts]], [[Current Contents]], [[EMBASE]], [[CAB Direct (database)|Global Health]], [[MEDLINE]], [[Science Citation Index]], and [[Scopus]].

